room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Escape Evansville in Evansville
room_description: You and your friends discover a boarded up cabin at Scales Lake. Upon entering the door slams and you get locked in for the night... And then you see him! Do you and your friends have what it takes to solve the puzzles, outsmart and keep away from the killer, and get out before the Cabin Fever claims another victim!
